OL,3,CSecond man dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed that a second
OL,7,Fman has now died following a collision
OL,8,Fon the A1(M) near Chester-le-Street in
OL,9,FCounty Durham on Sunday night (26
OL,10,FApril).
OL,12,FIt happened on the northbound
OL,13,Fcarriageway between junctions 62 and
OL,14,F63 at around 10.50pm.
OL,16,FOfficers believe a black Mercedes A
OL,17,FClass struck the central reservation,
OL,18,Fbefore coming to rest on its roof.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
