CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777551071
OL,3,CSecond man dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FThe road was closed in both directions
OL,7,Ffor around 12 hours, and reopened on
OL,8,FMonday lunchtime.
OL,10,FThree occupants were in the car at the
OL,11,Ftime of the collision.
OL,13,FThe driver of the car, a 20-year-old
OL,14,Fman, sustained critical injuries and
OL,15,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FMeanwhile a second man, also aged 20,
OL,18,Fsustained life-threatening injuries
OL,19,Fand was taken to Newcastle's Royal
OL,20,FVictoria Infirmary.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
