PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777551071
OL,3,CSecond man dies after crash on A1M in
OL,4,CCounty Durham
OL,6,FHe died as a result of his injuries on
OL,7,FMonday evening (27 April).
OL,9,FDurham Constabulary say their families
OL,10,Fhave been informed and are being
OL,11,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,12,Fofficers.
OL,14,FA third man sustained serious injuries
OL,15,Fand was taken hospital for treatment,
OL,16,Fwhere he remains in a stable condition.
OL,18,FOfficers are keen to speak to anyone
OL,19,Fwho witnessed the collision, or anyone
OL,20,Fwho may have dashcam footage of the
OL,21,Fvehicle prior to the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
